{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, in contrast to [ACC + 19], we do not provide details for any particular FHE construction or cryptanalytic attack.",
    "Instead, we encourage readers to consult the existing literature for detailed information on these aspects.",
    "There are many other works in the literature on subjects that are similar to, but not directly addressed by, this document.",
    "Here we present an overview of these topics.",
    "The NTRU problem [HPS98] is another widely used assumption in lattice-based cryptography."
  ]
}